---
import Layout from '../layouts/Layout.astro';
import Header from '../components/Header.astro';
import Footer from '../components/Footer.astro';
---

<Layout title="Frequently Asked Questions | Author's Choice" description="Find answers to the most common questions about Author's Choice technical writing program.">
  <Header />

  <section id="faq" class="faq section-lg">
    <div class="container">
      <div class="faq-header">
        <h2 class="section-title">
          Frequently Asked <span class="text-gradient">Questions</span>
        </h2>
        <p class="faq-subtitle">
          Get answers to the most common questions about our technical writing program.
        </p>
      </div>

      <div class="faq-grid">
        <div class="faq-item card fade-in">
          <div class="faq-question">
            <h3>Do I need a tech background to become a technical writer?</h3>
            <span class="faq-toggle">+</span>
          </div>
          <div class="faq-answer">
            <p>Absolutely not! Many of our most successful students came from non-tech backgrounds. Technical writing is about communication skills, not coding skills. We teach you how to understand and explain technical concepts without needing to be a developer yourself.</p>
          </div>
        </div>

        <div class="faq-item card fade-in">
          <div class="faq-question">
            <h3>How long does it take to get a job after completing the program?</h3>
            <span class="faq-toggle">+</span>
          </div>
          <div class="faq-answer">
            <p>Most students start applying around weeks 8-10 while still in the program. On average, our graduates receive job offers within 30-90 days of completing the program. Some land offers in as little as 6-8 weeks.</p>
          </div>
        </div>

        <div class="faq-item card fade-in">
          <div class="faq-question">
            <h3>What if I'm not a great writer? Can I still succeed?</h3>
            <span class="faq-toggle">+</span>
          </div>
          <div class="faq-answer">
            <p>Technical writing is different from creative writing. It's about clarity, structure, and following templates. If you can communicate clearly and follow instructions, you can learn technical writing. We provide templates, examples, and feedback to help you improve.</p>
          </div>
        </div>

        <div class="faq-item card fade-in">
          <div class="faq-question">
            <h3>Can I do this program while working full-time?</h3>
            <span class="faq-toggle">+</span>
          </div>
          <div class="faq-answer">
            <p>Yes! The program is designed for working professionals. You can complete the coursework at your own pace with approximately 5-8 hours of study per week. All coaching calls are recorded if you can't attend live.</p>
          </div>
        </div>

        <div class="faq-item card fade-in">
          <div class="faq-question">
            <h3>What's the difference between technical writing and content writing?</h3>
            <span class="faq-toggle">+</span>
          </div>
          <div class="faq-answer">
            <p>Technical writing focuses on instructional content like user guides, API documentation, and process documentation. It's more structured, pays significantly more, and is in higher demand than general content writing.</p>
          </div>
        </div>

        <div class="faq-item card fade-in">
          <div class="faq-question">
            <h3>Do you guarantee job placement?</h3>
            <span class="faq-toggle">+</span>
          </div>
          <div class="faq-answer">
            <p>While we can't guarantee job placement (no ethical program can), we have a 90% success rate. We provide all the tools, training, and support you need to succeed. Your success depends on your commitment to completing the program and applying what you learn.</p>
          </div>
        </div>

        <div class="faq-item card fade-in">
          <div class="faq-question">
            <h3>Is there ongoing support after the program ends?</h3>
            <span class="faq-toggle">+</span>
          </div>
          <div class="faq-answer">
            <p>Yes! You keep access to our private community, coach replays, and bonus resources. We also provide career advancement guidance as you grow in your technical writing career.</p>
          </div>
        </div>

        <div class="faq-item card fade-in">
          <div class="faq-question">
            <h3>What if I want to freelance instead of getting a job?</h3>
            <span class="faq-toggle">+</span>
          </div>
          <div class="faq-answer">
            <p>Perfect! We cover both paths. You'll learn how to find high-paying freelance clients, price your services competitively, and build long-term client relationships. Many of our students earn $75-150/hour as freelance technical writers.</p>
          </div>
        </div>

        <div class="faq-item card fade-in">
          <div class="faq-question">
            <h3>What tools and software will I need to learn?</h3>
            <span class="faq-toggle">+</span>
          </div>
          <div class="faq-answer">
            <p>We cover the most commonly used tools like Confluence, Notion, Google Docs, and basic screen recording software. Most tools are free or have free versions. We focus on principles over specific tools since companies use different platforms.</p>
          </div>
        </div>

        <div class="faq-item card fade-in">
          <div class="faq-question">
            <h3>How much can I expect to earn as a technical writer?</h3>
            <span class="faq-toggle">+</span>
          </div>
          <div class="faq-answer">
            <p>We will teach you 4-5 years worth of experience for an Entry-level technical writers position. With experience, you can earn $100K-$150K+ annually. Freelance technical writers often charge $75-$150 per hour. Remote work is common, offering additional flexibility and savings.</p>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>
       <div class="program-cta fade-in">
      <h3>Ready to Transform Your Writing Career?</h3>
      <p>Join our next cohort and start earning what you're worth as a technical writer.</p>
      <a href="#enroll" class="btn btn-primary btn-lg">Join Now</a>
    </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <Footer />
</Layout>

<style>
  .faq {
    background: var(--bg-primary);
  }

  .faq-header {
    text-align: center;
    margin-bottom: 4rem;
  }

  .section-title {
    font-size: 2.5rem;
    font-weight: 700;
    margin-bottom: 1rem;
    color: var(--text-primary);
  }

  .faq-subtitle {
    font-size: 1.25rem;
    color: var(--text-secondary);
    max-width: 600px;
    margin: 0 auto;
  }

  .faq-grid {
    display: grid;
    grid-template-columns: repeat(auto-fit, minmax(500px, 1fr));
    gap: 1.5rem;
    max-width: 1000px;
    margin: 0 auto;
    margin-bottom: 4rem;
  }

  .faq-item {
    padding: 1.5rem;
    cursor: pointer;
    transition: all 0.3s ease;
  }

  .faq-item:hover {
    transform: translateY(-2px);
  }

  .faq-question {
    display: flex;
    justify-content: space-between;
    align-items: center;
    margin-bottom: 1rem;
  }

  .faq-question h3 {
    font-size: 1.125rem;
    font-weight: 600;
    color: var(--text-primary);
    margin: 0;
    padding-right: 1rem;
  }

  .faq-toggle {
    background: #1e3a8a;
    color: white;
    width: 2rem;
    height: 2rem;
    border-radius: 50%;
    display: flex;
    align-items: center;
    justify-content: center;
    font-size: 1.25rem;
    font-weight: bold;
    flex-shrink: 0;
    transition: transform 0.3s ease;
  }

  .faq-answer {
    max-height: 0;
    overflow: hidden;
    transition: max-height 0.3s ease;
  }

  .faq-answer p {
    color: var(--text-secondary);
    line-height: 1.6;
    margin: 0;
    padding-bottom: 1rem;
  }

  .faq-item.active .faq-toggle {
    transform: rotate(45deg);
    background: #f97316;
  }

  .faq-item.active .faq-answer {
    max-height: 200px;
  }

  @media (max-width: 768px) {
    .section-title {
      font-size: 2rem;
    }

    .faq-grid {
      grid-template-columns: 1fr;
    }

    .faq-question h3 {
      font-size: 1rem;
    }
  }



 .program-cta {
    text-align: center;
    background: linear-gradient(135deg, #1e3a8a 0%, #3b82f6 100%);
    padding: 3rem 2rem;
    border-radius: 1rem;
    color: white;
    position: relative;
    overflow: hidden;
  }

  .program-cta::before {
    content: '';
    position: absolute;
    top: -50%;
    left: -50%;
    width: 200%;
    height: 200%;
    background: radial-gradient(circle, rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.1) 0%, transparent 70%);
    animation: rotate 20s linear infinite;
  }

  @keyframes rotate {
    0% {
      transform: rotate(0deg);
    }
    100% {
      transform: rotate(360deg);
    }
  }

  .program-cta h3 {
    font-size: 2rem;
    font-weight: 700;
    margin-bottom: 1rem;
    position: relative;
    z-index: 1;
  }

  .program-cta p {
    font-size: 1.25rem;
    margin-bottom: 2rem;
    opacity: 0.9;
    position: relative;
    z-index: 1;
  }

  .program-cta .btn {
    position: relative;
    z-index: 1;
  }

  @media (max-width: 768px) {
    .section-title {
      font-size: 2rem;
    }

    .program-subtitle {
      font-size: 1.125rem;
    }

    .program-modules {
      grid-template-columns: 1fr;
    }

    .program-cta h3 {
      font-size: 1.5rem;
    }

    .program-cta p {
      font-size: 1.125rem;
    }

    .module-card:hover {
      transform: translateY(-4px) scale(1.01);
    }
  }

</style>

<script>
  document.addEventListener('DOMContentLoaded', function() {
    const faqItems = document.querySelectorAll('.faq-item');
    
    faqItems.forEach(item => {
      item.addEventListener('click', function() {
        const isActive = this.classList.contains('active');
        
        // Close all other items
        faqItems.forEach(otherItem => {
          otherItem.classList.remove('active');
        });
        
        // Toggle current item
        if (!isActive) {
          this.classList.add('active');
        }
      });
    });
  });
</script>